Date: 1992-06-24

Title: Time Travel?

Authors: Stanley Deser and Roman Jackiw

Comments: 19 double-spaced pages

Journal-ref: Comments Nucl.Part.Phys. 20 (1992) 337

To travel into the past, to observe it, perhaps to influence it and correctmistakes of one's youth, has been an abiding fantasy of mankind for as long aswe have been aware of a past. Here are described some recent scientificinvestigations on this topic.